{"tid":1016715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山客城門水塘郊遊　驚見男子上吊亡","createTime":"2019-02-11T02:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T02:22:18.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e039c9352170daac808dbf0a6a5da34141bb224","tid":1016715,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"荃灣城門水塘賞蝶園，今早(11日)7時26分，一名男子被行山人士發現以尼龍繩，掛於一個休憩亭的木架上自縊，警方及消防接報趕至，將男子解下，證實已告氣絕身亡。警方在現場檢獲懷疑遺書以及一個藍色背包，相信是死者留下。 <br />\n<br />\n警員又在附近的枱櫈上發現數罐啤酒，相信死者曾飲酒澆愁，正調查其尋死原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190211/mobile/bkn-20190211074646344-0211_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190211%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190211074646344-0211_00822_001.html&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo534IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=7442aef7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190211/mobile/bkn-20190211074646344-0211_00822_001.html</a>"}]}